{"tid":612175,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"玻璃之城(1998)20周年","createTime":"2018-03-31T16:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T16:16:14.000Z","uid":122625,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f8c7d1f5c705501acdde2784c20f1f100067c93c","tid":612175,"uid":122625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T16:16:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/234645_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F234645_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6a147503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知仲有冇人記得呢齣戲<br />\n電影唻講唔算出色<br />\n<br />\n例如黎明係好文質彬彬<br />\n但冇許港生嗰種kong u天之驕子嘅狂妄<br />\n舒琪好靚 但講對白嘅語氣唔見得係個有書卷氣嘅角色<br />\n<br />\n雖然講97過渡<br />\n但唔覺得同主線愛情線有扣連到<br />\n<br />\n吳彥祖一開頭講 &ldquo;香港係件亮晶晶嘅垃圾&rdquo; <br />\n之後劇情冇平反亦冇加以描述<br />\n<br />\n但種種元素加埋<br />\n就令呢成為一齣好睇 今時今日睇返有種aftertaste嘅電影<br />\n<br />\nHku背景 殖民地色彩<br />\n舒琪黎明呢個可一不可再嘅組合<br />\n<br />\n睇住主角撞完車死先倒敍返佢地點結識<br />\n一場喺電影開始時已注定要完結嘅戀情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/234655_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F234655_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=cb2df1ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/234705_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F234705_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c4729a83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/001156_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F001156_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=350cb7f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有eason<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/001230_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F001230_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=91add316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張燊悅靚唔靚就見仁見智 不過起碼係香港演員 睇得舒服<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/001320_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F001320_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7787a103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有巔峰期靚仔嘅吳彥祖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}